Class WriteAheadLogReader

  • Object
    • org.apache.spark.streaming.util.WriteAheadLogReader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Closeable, AutoCloseable, Logging, scala.collection.GenTraversableOnce<java.nio.ByteBuffer>, scala.collection.Iterator<java.nio.ByteBuffer>, scala.collection.TraversableOnce<java.nio.ByteBuffer>

    public class WriteAheadLogReader
extends Object
implements scala.collection.Iterator<java.nio.ByteBuffer>, java.io.Closeable, Logging
    A reader for reading write ahead log files written using WriteAheadLogWriter. This reads the records (bytebuffers) in the log file sequentially and return them as an iterator of bytebuffers.
